395
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:37,580
We won't give up until the very last moment.

396
00:31:37,580 --> 00:31:39,830
Young Lady Jun, you'd better leave soon.

397
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:42,670
Lord Lu has prepared a hideout already.

398
00:31:42,670 --> 00:31:46,170
If we leave now, nobody will notice it or blame you.

399
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:49,750
Once the city is stormed, His Majesty won't come back for real.

400
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:52,410
That's why we must keep the Chu family's descendants safe.

401
00:31:52,410 --> 00:31:55,600
Prince Huai, as the heir of the late emperor, has a good reputation.

402
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:59,350
Some things should be done in a certain way.

403
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:04,230
- Master Gu–
- Hurry!

404
00:32:04,230 --> 00:32:08,240
Young Lady Jun, it looks like Northern Qi is really storming the city. If you don't leave, it'll be too late.

405
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,620
You don't need to say anymore.

406
00:32:09,620 --> 00:32:13,300
I know what you mean. Please tell Lord Lu that I won't leave.

407
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:17,040
Jiurong is guarding the city, not because of reputation or the throne.

408
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:19,320
This city has protected us for years.

409
00:32:19,320 --> 00:32:22,720
The descendants of the Chu family must defend it at all costs and not shirk their responsibilities.

410
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:25,250
If you're not staying behind, go ahead and leave.

