00:32:25,250 --> 00:32:27,010
Young Lady Jun!

412
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:16,890
Kill!

413
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:40,750
Let's go!

414
00:33:45,190 --> 00:33:47,110
