415
00:33:53,850 --> 00:33:56,460
Don't run! Catch him!

416
00:33:58,230 --> 00:34:00,750
Protect Prince Huai!

417
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:19,160
Everyone can kill the enemy!

418
00:34:20,680 --> 00:34:26,330
Everyone can kill the enemy!

